1... g5 $3 {Preventing White from playing g5! After that, we plan to play ...
Ba6- Nf8-Ng6-h8!-f7-d8-b7-a5 and c4 drops!} 2. Bd3 Ba6 $19 {[%csl Ga6,Rc4,Gd7]
