8. bxc3 d6 9. e4 e5 10. d5 Ne7 11. Nh4 Ng6 12. Nf5 Nf4 13. Bxf4 {A bad choice,
but at the same time a move that many White players may choose.} exf4 14. Qf3
g5 15. h4 Bxf5 ({Strictly speaking} 15... Nd7 $17 {is the best. White is in
