Kf1 $2 {White misses the opponent's forced win. The situation was already
tough, though.} Nde3+ 27. fxe3 Nxe3+ 28. Ke2 Nxd1 29. Rc2 Rxd4 30. Nd2 Rxd2+
31. Rxd2 Rxd2+ 32. Kxd2 Nxb2 33. Kc3 Na4+ 34. Kb4 Nb6 0-1

