1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. e3 O-O 5. Nge2 (5. Bd3 d5 (5... c5) 6. cxd5
exd5 7. Nge2 Re8 8. Bd2) 5... d5 6. cxd5 $6 {a bad move!} (6. a3 Be7 (6... Bd6
7. c5) 7. Nf4 c6 8. Be2 Nbd7 9. O-O dxc4 10. Bxc4 e5 11. Nfe2 exd4 12. exd4 (
12. Nxd4 Ne5) 12... Nb6 13. Bb3 Bf5) 6... exd5 7. g3 (7. a3 Bd6 $1 8. Nb5 (8.
Ng3 c6 $15) 8... Be7 $1 {i had him play Nb5, and only now i go Be7 !}) (7. a3
Be7 8. g3 Nbd7 9. Bg2 Nb6 10. O-O a5 11. b3 Re8 12. a4 c6) 7... Re8 (7... c6)
8. Bg2 a5 $5 (8... c6 9. O-O) 9. O-O c6 10. a3 Bd6 11. f3 c5 $1 12. Bd2 (12.
Nb5 Bf8 13. Bd2 b6 $17 (13... Nc6 $17 14. Re1 b6 15. Rc1 (15. dxc5 bxc5 $1 $17
(15... Bxc5 $15)) 15... Ba6 $15)) 12... Nc6 13. Rc1 b6 $1 (13... cxd4 $2 {
black should keep the tension in the center!} 14. exd4) 14. Nb5 (14. dxc5 bxc5)
14... Bf8 15. a4 Ba6 16. Re1 Nb4 $17 (16... Bxb5 17. axb5 Nb4 $17) 17. Bxb4
axb4 18. Nf4 Bxb5 19. axb5 Ra2 20. Rc2 Qd7 21. Bf1 b3 22. Rc1 c4 23. e4 Rxb2
24. exd5 g5 25. Ng2 Rxe1 26. Qxe1 Qf5 27. Ne3 Qxf3 28. Nxc4 Rc2 29. Rb1 Ng4 30.
Rb2 Bb4 31. Be2 Qf6 0-1

