Nbd7 {...b5 is the best move!} 9. Be2 exd5 10. cxd5 a6 11. O-O Ne5 (11... Nf8 {
usually we should go from f8 to avoid f4.}) 12. f4 Ng6 13. Bd3 b5 14. a3 Ba5
15. Bc2 Bd7 16. g4 $2 {major mistake! White is weakning his own King.} h6 17.
e5 Bxc3 18. bxc3 dxe5 19. g5 Nh7 20. Qh5 exf4 21. h4 hxg5 22. hxg5 Nxg5 23. Kh2
