Bg2 Nxe1 {Black is clearly better.}) 24... Nxd4 25. cxd4 Nf3+ 26. Kf2 Qxh2+ 27.
Bg2 Nxe1 28. Kxe1 Qg1+ 29. Bf1 Bh3 30. Qf2 Qh1 31. Ba3 Bxf1 32. Qxf1 Qc6 0-1

